						<div class="postbody">Merge the sword with the &quot;R&quot; in &quot;Rodas&quot;, and make the sword/R take up the entire height of the text (both lines).  I'm not an artist, but this is what I'm referring to:<br /><div class="attachtitle">Attachment:</div><div class="attachcontent">
			<img src="./download/file.php?id=12156" alt="Untitled.png" /><br />
			<span class="gensmall">Untitled.png [ 8.92 KiB | Viewed 2443 times ]</span>
		

		<br />
	</div><br /><br />You might also experiment with the &quot;C&quot; in Cross being somehow merged with the lower curve of the sword/R, but that might look tacky.  From a graphic design/signage standpoint (I worked at an engraving company for some time, and my mother owned one for 30+ years), it would probably be hard to read.</div>

